Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.90,0:01:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真得受不了了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.10,0:01:51.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想就這樣死掉
