Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.80,0:02:02.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想再忍受更多痛苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.30,0:02:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至少可以把所有的一切都忘掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.70,0:02:11.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第十六話 追憶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.70,0:02:31.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你醒了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.30,0:02:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是哪里？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.30,0:02:50.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在你的房間裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.20,0:02:55.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是誰？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.80,0:02:59.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lumiere 你的搭檔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.10,0:03:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搭檔？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.00,0:03:04.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lumiere…然後什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.90,0:03:07.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有Lumiere而已啊 Eclair
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.50,0:03:10.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eclair？ 那是我的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.30,0:03:13.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是你的名字 Eclair
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.30,0:03:25.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這就是…我？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.60,0:03:29.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這樣年紀的女孩子可不能這麼做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.20,0:03:32.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要碰我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.50,0:03:37.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eclair…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.20,0:03:44.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種力量是什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.40,0:03:50.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eclair…那就是我的名字嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.70,0:03:52.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.50,0:03:53.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eclair…然後什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.80,0:03:55.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有Eclair而已啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.80,0:03:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別開玩笑了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.70,0:04:00.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼這種力量又是什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.40,0:04:06.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是你的才能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.40,0:04:08.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,騙人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.80,0:04:10.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,騙人 騙人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.90,0:04:11.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,騙人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.60,0:04:23.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是誰？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.70,0:04:25.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼人？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.50,0:04:26.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我會…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.30,0:04:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我比任何人都瞭解你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.10,0:04:34.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,力量強 速度快 還很溫柔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.40,0:04:38.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這些事我會一點一點地告訴你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.40,0:04:40.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,騙人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.10,0:04:44.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我絕對不會騙你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.40,0:04:49.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直相信你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.80,0:05:15.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.60,0:05:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,倒是你沒問題了吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.60,0:05:25.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題吧 Eclair？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.40,0:05:27.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.10,0:05:30.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來我至少還記得如何沐浴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.30,0:05:34.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eclair
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.70,0:05:37.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我的名字是男孩的名字…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.20,0:05:41.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但感覺好像在某個地方聽過好多次了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.30,0:05:44.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我把毛巾放這兒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.90,0:05:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.20,0:05:49.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感覺好極了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.40,0:05:51.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.40,0:05:56.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之 得先解決你的穿著問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.60,0:06:08.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這些都是你的衣服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.90,0:06:19.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們還是先吃些東西吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.20,0:06:32.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,女孩子要優雅些
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.40,0:06:37.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請稍等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.10,0:06:45.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你很喜歡嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.30,0:06:47.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 十分喜歡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.60,0:06:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你畢竟是個女孩子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.00,0:06:53.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過 既然是女孩子就要更優雅些
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.10,0:06:56.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,優雅…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.80,0:07:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你必須學很多東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.50,0:07:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了代替過去的記憶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.60,0:07:06.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,代替過去的記憶？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.50,0:07:09.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是奇怪的說法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.90,0:07:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 我說錯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.70,0:07:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該說為了使你恢復記憶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.20,0:07:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼不對嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.60,0:07:22.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒 你果然是我的搭檔啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.10,0:07:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知為何我十分安心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.50,0:07:29.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝 很高興聽你這麼說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.90,0:07:32.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個人是誰？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.40,0:07:34.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eclipse
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.10,0:07:36.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她是我們的所屬機關
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.90,0:07:41.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,銀河通商關稅機構-GOTT總局的局長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.10,0:07:44.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是漂亮的人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.10,0:07:46.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你早晚會見到她的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.60,0:07:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個建築物呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.10,0:07:51.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,GOTT總局
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.20,0:07:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也是兼管Aineias上一切事物的行政機關
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.90,0:07:59.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了 接下來學習歷史吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.00,0:08:07.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.40,0:08:09.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真的可以外出嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.30,0:08:23.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓你久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.30,0:08:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裏早上幾點開門？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.60,0:08:29.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,6:30 不過6點以後就開門了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.50,0:08:31.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.80,0:08:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們可以來這裏吃早飯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.20,0:08:37.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兩位客人是第一次來本店吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.10,0:08:38.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是姐妹嗎？
