Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.60,0:08:52.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望你能經常來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.80,0:08:56.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是卡普里斯 是店裏的看板娘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.40,0:08:59.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請多關照 我是Eclair
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.30,0:09:01.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個孩子是我妹妹Lumiere
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.80,0:09:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡普里斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.00,0:09:05.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.50,0:09:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請慢用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.60,0:09:14.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我做得沒錯吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.30,0:09:15.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,合格了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.50,0:09:18.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 你說的獨自生活是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.70,0:09:21.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你已經沒問題了對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.50,0:09:24.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,過一陣子我會再來看你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.80,0:09:28.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓你久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.20,0:09:34.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來了 來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.20,0:09:40.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lumiere 進來進來 我去倒咖啡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.00,0:09:41.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用那麼麻煩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.30,0:09:45.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼不適應的地方嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.60,0:09:46.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一點也沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.70,0:09:49.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我對於你給的訓練表已經厭煩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.70,0:09:52.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這些照片是什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.00,0:09:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.40,0:09:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朋友…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.40,0:09:58.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你喜歡拍照嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.20,0:10:01.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.00,0:10:07.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是希望不會再忘記他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.70,0:10:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣嗎…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.50,0:10:20.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎… 她叫Donnerschlag啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.10,0:10:24.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請多關照 Donner
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.50,0:10:25.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是Eclair
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.50,0:10:37.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得有似曾相識的感覺啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.00,0:10:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這支最適合我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.50,0:10:56.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過缺少了些東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.90,0:11:03.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是你的槍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.60,0:11:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.70,0:11:18.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.80,0:11:21.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eclair、Lumiere
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.30,0:11:58.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是銀河通商關稅機構 GOTT所屬ES成員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.40,0:12:04.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eclair和Lumiere的最新監視報告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.70,0:12:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至於檔的時間標記
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.00,0:12:09.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在記錄檔案的不同層面上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.00,0:12:11.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,準備了不可修改的一份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.60,0:12:15.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不需要那樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.20,0:12:18.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正是因為我相信你的人格
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.10,0:12:20.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以才拜託你執行這個任務
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.70,0:12:22.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是我的榮幸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.40,0:12:30.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以下摘錄上次報告以後發生的主要事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.30,0:12:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,首先應該是Faunus-Medeia危機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.30,0:12:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了避免商業行星Faunus 和礦業行星Medeia之間發生衝突
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.50,0:12:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原本任務目的是簽訂談判協定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.00,0:12:44.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過您也知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.20,0:12:50.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不如說解決操縱Faunus的兩派貴族間的爭執
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.30,0:12:52.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可能比較妥當
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.30,0:12:56.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們讓你在這一事件中經歷了很多麻煩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.40,0:12:57.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.00,0:12:59.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請您別這麼說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.10,0:13:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後是馬克思事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.90,0:13:10.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,逮捕十名非法製造 販賣重力控制物質Hi-G的貴族後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.70,0:13:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她們捲入了揭露Shopper這類犯罪組織的事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.10,0:13:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以及處理貴族子女失蹤事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.20,0:13:25.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rosenfelt家族繼承者事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.40,0:13:29.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在那個時候 我們可以看出金融管理局的敵對態度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.30,0:13:35.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而結果是GOTT贏得貿易上的有利因素
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.60,0:13:36.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.80,0:13:40.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後是非法產品Geo-Sorter炸彈事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.00,0:13:42.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她們也捲入那起事件了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.90,0:13:43.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.50,0:13:47.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那件事大概是貴族們操縱的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.30,0:13:51.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過一個星球 被徹底毀滅了的事實是無法隱藏的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.20,0:13:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是一件眾所周知的事 不過知道真相的人大概不多吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.90,0:14:00.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,隨後是行星Dardanos
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.60,0:14:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是一個試驗區嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.40,0:14:04.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,試驗區？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.50,0:14:07.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你這樣想？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.40,0:14:10.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誘導民眾意識的試驗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.20,0:14:15.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我猜那是支配銀河系的貴族們幹的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.00,0:14:18.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那不是全體貴族的意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.60,0:14:23.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是統治Dardanos的人的愚蠢行為造成的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.60,0:14:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當局已經讓他們得到了應有的懲罰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.60,0:14:32.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過連Dardanos事件也捲入
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.80,0:14:36.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該說是因果報應？ 我感覺到有某種宿命的存在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.10,0:14:41.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事情會是GOTT總局局長堅持的那樣嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.80,0:14:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.10,0:14:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個我也不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.50,0:14:48.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至少行星Aure事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.70,0:14:50.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是她堅持的那樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.60,0:14:53.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秘密花園嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.60,0:14:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也很吃驚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.30,0:15:01.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當中央委員會成員提到 Eclair這個名字時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.20,0:15:05.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼這件事的報告…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.50,0:15:06.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不必說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.50,0:15:09.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已經知道了詳細的情況
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.10,0:15:11.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的是很悲哀啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.70,0:15:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.40,0:15:16.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,消除命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.00,0:15:20.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說得到了死刑命令 兩人開始逃亡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.10,0:15:25.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她們設法躲過了 GOTT SO成員和ES成員的追擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.20,0:15:32.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是機器人護衛 和專用高速巡洋艦的AI被控制了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.40,0:15:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被強迫和她們戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.50,0:15:40.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當時我沒有跟著她們 所以不知道詳情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.50,0:15:42.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結果很明顯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.50,0:15:46.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,造成她們兩個攻擊GOTT總部的事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.20,0:15:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然有三對ES成員阻止她們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.00,0:15:54.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,GOTT毀滅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.70,0:16:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,關於每個事件的詳細情報 我都整理在檔裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.50,0:16:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.10,0:16:26.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.00,0:16:29.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不必客氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.80,0:16:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼現在Aineias的情況如何？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.60,0:16:45.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,GOTT目前正在重建
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.60,0:16:47.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,局長Eclipse死亡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.20,0:16:52.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,暫時從ES成員中選出了一個代理局長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.70,0:16:56.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,代理局長？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.00,0:16:57.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.50,0:17:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖說是選出 實際上是行星聯盟評議會指明的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.70,0:17:07.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,行星聯盟評議會的人嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.20,0:17:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼是誰？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.70,0:17:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被選上的是誰？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.40,0:17:15.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是Eclair
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.40,0:17:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說她是個自主的新局長也沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.60,0:17:24.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eclair…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.70,0:17:30.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.70,0:17:35.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她用倒塌在總部大樓旁的附屬建築物 作為臨時辦公室
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.10,0:17:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,並且已經開始活動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.00,0:17:40.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.70,0:17:42.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反應真的很快呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.30,0:17:49.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她們還組織了十二名新的ES成員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.90,0:17:52.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,試圖增強自主的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.80,0:17:54.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖說如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.20,0:17:57.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實是改編以前全部的ES成員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.10,0:18:07.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在Atlas級宇宙船建造即將完成的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.60,0:18:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是件棘手的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.70,0:18:18.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就是你派遣我們的原因吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.10,0:18:21.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那不是唯一的原因
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.90,0:18:25.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請繼續監視她們的動靜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.10,0:18:31.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.10,0:18:36.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,告辭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.00,0:18:45.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是個比我想像的還要笨的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.10,0:18:48.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過我也沒資格評論別人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.50,0:18:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,資料傳輸 使用G5級秘密線路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.20,0:19:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很久不見了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.50,0:19:24.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉讓你幹這樣的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.30,0:19:27.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請別說見外的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.00,0:19:30.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們從中學時代起就是朋友了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.90,0:19:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.50,0:19:37.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看上去GOTT遇到大麻煩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.20,0:19:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.30,0:19:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且很可疑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.10,0:19:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說是行星聯盟評議會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.40,0:19:47.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實是中央委員會的別名罷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.30,0:19:50.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過如果他們參與的話…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.70,0:19:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我早有心理準備了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.10,0:19:55.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.10,0:19:57.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我保證我不再參與此事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.10,0:20:01.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是你為什麼不自己調查呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.00,0:20:05.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你能看到你的後背嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.00,0:20:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.90,0:20:10.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.60,0:20:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會再和你聯絡的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.60,0:20:16.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.60,0:20:18.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我衷心的感謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.30,0:20:22.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.30,0:20:28.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來我想阻止你也沒有用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.20,0:20:30.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過請別做魯莽的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.20,0:20:34.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為你是我為數不多的好友了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.30,0:20:38.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也祝你好運
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.00,0:21:14.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eclair嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.50,0:21:59.29,SongChn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14}就這樣走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.50,0:21:59.29,SongRom,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\k40\k40}sa {\k40}a {\k30}{\k40}yu {\k40}ko {\k10}u
